des: "Cincinnati brings you this classic chili dip--with a McCormickÂ® twist! Mix lean ground beef with McCormickÂ® Original Chili Seasoning Mix and cinnamon. Top with Cheddar cheese, onion and serve warm. Master your dip-dunking skills with pasta chips or potato chips."
ins:
Brown ground beef in large skillet on medium-high heat until beef is no longer pink, about 5 minutes. Drain fat.
Stir tomato sauce, chili seasoning, and cinnamon into the skillet. Bring to boil. Reduce heat to low; simmer 10 minutes. Sprinkle with Cheddar cheese and onion.
